title: Human Events Special - FBI: American Stasi
description:
FBI: AMERICAN STASI! Former President Donald Trump announced that the FBI raided his ‘beautiful home’ in Mar-a-Lago, breaking into his safe and taking several documents; however, Hunter Biden remains in the clear despite the release of the contents on his laptop. Hillary Clinton has escaped the FBI after they overlooked Russiagate and her email server scandal. Jack argues that FBI movies and shows are purely fairy tales for adults, then exposes historical facts proving the FBI aren’t as virtuous as they are portrayed to be. 



Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
